  "id": "RAW_0a7dcb",
  "title": "探索智能的边界：DeepMind 掌舵人德米斯·哈萨比斯的终极蓝图  | 附 4 万字访谈全文",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&mid=2247488750&idx=1&sn=617b25c07a43af9bf3b56df687afad70",
  "date": "2025-07-24 15:58:00",
  "author": "Web3天空之城",
  "siteName": "Web3天空之城",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><span style=\"background-color: inherit; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.1em;\">文:Web3天空之城.城主</span></p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100005099\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7460bfd9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FV08icaMk7MVaXjr0hcCcICXicstGibnmzkePKHETvroqzePpMOxO6WlpVeyZ6KUxUqcWQyJMno5CYhvl6uDSqU1Og%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在与Lex Fridman的最新深度对话中，谷歌DeepMind的领导者、新晋诺贝尔奖得主德米斯·哈萨比斯（Demis Hassabis）以前所未有的系统性，揭示了他对人工智能、宇宙规律乃至人类文明未来的构想。哈萨比斯提出一个颠覆性猜想——一个“可学习的宇宙”。这一理论不仅是他解读AlphaFold等成就的哲学基石，更构成了他通往通用人工智能（AGI）并最终解决人类最根本挑战的清晰蓝图。从模拟物理世界、重塑交互娱乐，到驾驭能源危机和生命之谜，哈萨比斯正在为我们描绘的，是一个由AI驱动、彻底摆脱稀缺性限制的文明新纪元。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><span leaf=\"\">核心观点摘要</span></h3>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我的猜想是，自然界中可以生成或发现的任何模式，原则上都可以通过经典的机器学习算法有效地发现和建模。宇宙是一个信息系统，因此，P vs NP本质上是一个物理学问题，我认为这是最根本的问题之一。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“像VEO这样的视频生成模型，能够很好地模拟液体、材料和光照，这令人惊讶。这些系统本质上是在通过观看YouTube视频对物理学进行逆向工程。这暗示了关于现实本质的某些深层东西。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“选择正确的问题是科学中最难的部分。一个系统能否提出一个值得研究的猜想，比解决它要难得多。这是一种更高级的创造力，也是通往AGI路上的关键。今天的系统绝对无法做到这一点。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“在人类历史上，我们将第一次不受资源限制。如果我们能正确利用AI解决能源问题——无论是聚变还是太阳能——就能开启一个资源极大丰富的后稀缺时代，摆脱零和博弈。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我不认为这是一场竞赛。重要的是，我们所有处于领先地位的人，都有责任为了人类的利益，安全地将这项令人难以置信的技术引入世界。我希望最终国际社群能够团结起来。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“AI带来的变革，其影响可能相当于工业革命的10倍，但速度也快了10倍。这种影响与速度的乘积效应，将使社会更难应对。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“构建人工智能，然后将其与人类思维进行比较，将是揭示人类思维特殊之处的最佳方法。这会帮助我们理解当我们处理信息时，信息所感觉到的方式——也就是意识。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: none;height: 1px;color: inherit;margin: 2em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">一 | 哲思基石：一个“可学习的宇宙”</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">一切的起点，源于哈萨比斯在诺贝尔奖演讲上抛出的一个深刻猜想。他认为，宇宙中的自然模式——从蛋白质在我们体内毫秒级的折叠，到山脉在千万年风化中的形成——并非随机混沌，而是具有内在的“可学习性”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“自然系统具有结构，因为它们受到塑造它们的进化过程或‘最稳定者生存’法则的影响，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;哈萨比斯解释道，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“如果这是真的，那么应该存在某种低维流形（low-dimensional manifold），你可以逆向学习，它能帮助你高效地搜索到正确的解决方案，因为它不是随机模式。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">这一视角彻底重构了我们对AI能力的理解。无论是AlphaGo在围棋10^170种可能性中的惊天一手，还是AlphaFold在蛋白质10^300种构象中的精准预测，其本质都不是蛮力破解。相反，它们是通过构建环境的精确模型，在这个充满结构性的“景观”中，循着梯度进行智能搜索，从而将指数级复杂的NP难题，转化为多项式时间内可解的问题。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">这一思想的终极延伸，是将计算机科学的经典难题与宇宙的物理本质直接关联。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我一直对P=NP问题着迷，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;哈萨比斯说，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我倾向于认为信息是宇宙中最基本的单位，比能量和物质更基本。当你把宇宙看作一个信息系统时，那么P=NP就是一个物理学问题。我认为它的答案将会非常具有启发性。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在他看来，我们今天所见的AI奇迹，仅仅是经典图灵机潜能的冰山一角，而AGI将是这种潜能的终极体现。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">二 | 现实模拟：当AI成为世界的物理引擎</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">如果宇宙是可学习的，那么AI模拟物理世界的能力便有了理论根基。哈萨比斯眼中最震撼的例证，正是谷歌最新的视频生成模型VEO。当公众惊叹于其生成的喜剧短片时，这位前游戏物理引擎开发者却看到了更深层的东西。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我喜欢那些有人生成透明液体通过液压机被挤压的视频，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他分享道，带着一种技术专家的兴奋，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我早年在游戏行业编写过物理引擎，我知道构建能做到这一点的程序是多么令人费力。然而，不知何-何，这些系统正在通过观看YouTube视频对物理学进行逆向工程。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">VEO对流体、镜面反射和光照的精准模拟，意味着它已经内化了一种“直觉物理学”</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">（intuitive physics）——一种关于世界如何运作的常识性理解。这有力地挑战了“AI必须通过与物理世界直接互动才能获得理解”的传统“具身智能”理论。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">“看起来你可以通过被动观察来理解它，这对我来说非常令人惊讶，” 哈萨比斯坦言，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我认为这再次暗示了关于现实本质的某些深层东西。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">而这仅仅是开端。模拟一个静态的世界之后，下一步必然是与之互动。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">三 | 交互前沿：重塑娱乐与创造的未来</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">哈萨比斯对未来的构想，充满了他在游戏设计黄金时代（90年代）的激情。他曾主导开发了《主题公园》、《黑与白》等里程碑式的开放世界游戏，而如今，他认为AI将最终实现他当年的终极梦想：一个真正动态、个性化、由玩家与AI共同创造的无限世界。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">他精准地指出了当前开放世界游戏的局限——所谓的自由选择，往往只是精心设计的“选择的幻觉”，正如在经典游戏《史丹利的寓言》中所讽刺的那样。而未来的游戏将彻底打破这一桎梏。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“你希望能够在这个游戏环境中潜在地做任何事情，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他描绘道，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我认为实现这一点的唯一方法是拥有生成系统，即能够动态生成内容的系统……它能够动态地改变故事，围绕叙事进行讲述，并使其无论你最终选择什么都充满戏剧性。这就像终极的‘选择你自己的冒险’式游戏。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">想象一下，一个互动版的VEO，你不再是观看视频，而是可以走进视频，你的每一个行为都会引发世界合乎逻辑的、充满创造性的响应。这不仅将颠覆价值数千亿美元的娱乐产业，更预示着一种全新的创造范式——当每个人都能利用AI将想象力变为可交互的现实时，创造的门槛将被极大降低。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">四 | 通往AGI之路：超越规模与探寻“研究品味”</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">对于何时能实现通用人工智能（AGI），哈萨比斯给出了一个具体的概率预测：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“未来五年内有大约50%的几率，比如说，到2030年。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;但他反复强调，通往AGI的道路并非仅仅依赖于计算规模（Scale）的无限扩展。他认为，可能还需要类似于AlphaGo“第37步”棋那样的、能够跳出人类已知范畴的重大研究突破。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在这里，他引入了一个至关重要的概念：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“研究品味”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（Research Taste）。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我认为品味或判断力这个概念，将是最难模仿或建模的事情之一。它区分了伟大科学家和优秀科学家，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他深刻地指出，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“选择正确的问题是科学中最难的部分，以及提出正确的假设。一个系统能否提出一个值得研究的猜想，比解决它要难得多。这是一种更高级的创造力，也是今天的系统绝对无法做到的。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">他设想的AGI终极测试之一，就是看系统能否在拥有1900年前所有知识的情况下，独立推导出狭义与广义相对论。这考验的正是这种提出深刻、可证伪且能推动知识边界的假设的能力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">为了攀登这一高峰，DeepMind正双管齐下：一方面继续扩展模型规模，另一方面则通过AlphaEvolve（用LLM引导进化算法）、AlphaProof（解决数学奥林匹克难题）等项目，探索让AI系统实现创造力飞跃的全新路径。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">五 | 文明重构：作为终极工具的AGI</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在哈萨比斯的宏伟蓝图中，AGI并非终点，而是解决人类文明最根本挑战的“终极工具”。他个人职业生涯的梦想，是构建一个完整的“虚拟细胞”，以原子级的精度模拟细胞内部所有动态交互。他与导师、诺贝尔奖得主保罗·纳斯（Paul Nurse）探讨这个想法长达25年，而今天，随着AlphaFold 3开始模拟蛋白质间的复杂互动，这个梦想正变得触手可及。它有望将药物研发的速度提升百倍，彻底改变生命科学。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">目光放得更远，他相信AI将是破解能源危机的钥匙。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我认为聚变和太阳能是我会押注的两种能源，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他断言。AI可以帮助设计更优的聚变反应堆（DeepMind已与联邦聚变公司合作）、发现室温超导材料、或创造更高效的太阳能电池板。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“如果我们以其中一种方式解决了能源问题，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;哈萨比斯展望道，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“那么在人类历史上，我们将第一次不受资源限制。用水问题消失了，因为海水淡化变得廉价；我们拥有无限的火箭燃料。我认为这将开启一个资源极大丰富的后稀缺时代，摆脱零和博弈。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，这位乐观的远见者也发出了清醒的警告。他预见到，这场变革的社会冲击将是空前的。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我认为我们将看到的影响可能相当于工业革命的10倍，但速度也快了10倍，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他说，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“这种影响与速度的乘积效应，将使社会更难应对。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他呼吁全球顶级的经济学家、哲学家和政治家，现在就开始严肃思考如何设计新的社会契约和治理结构，以应对即将到来的大规模职业颠覆和财富分配挑战。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">结语：智能的责任与人性的回响</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">尽管身处一场被外界描绘为“军备竞赛”的科技浪潮中心，哈萨比斯却始终保持着一种科学家的冷静与责任感。他将领导DeepMind的经历比作运营一家“大规模的创业公司”，在庞大的谷歌体系内保持着果断与活力。但他拒绝用“获胜”来定义自己的目标。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我不认为这是一场竞赛，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他郑重地表示，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“重要的是，我们所有处于领先地位的人，都有责任为了人类的利益，安全地将这项令人难以置信的技术引入世界。我希望最终国际社群能够团结起来，当越来越接近AGI时，人们会明显地意识到这是必需的。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在他看来，这段探索人工智能边界的旅程，最终也将引领我们回到对自身的审视。正如他所引用的理查德·费曼的名言——“我无法创造的，我就不理解”，哈萨比斯相信，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“构建人工智能，然后将其与人类思维进行比较，将是揭示人类思维特殊之处的最佳方法。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这或许关乎意识的本质，关乎碳基生命与硅基智能处理信息时那“感觉到的方式”的奥秘。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">原访谈4万字全文传送:</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&amp;mid=2247488745&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d5bd853a68b8ae849a79590f84095b06&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"探索智能的边界：DeepMind领导者德米斯·哈萨比斯最新对话录| 4万字完整版\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">探索智能的边界：DeepMind领导者德米斯·哈萨比斯最新对话录| 4万字完整版</a></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "Demis Hassabis 在访谈中阐述了其“可学习宇宙”理论，并描绘了 AI 如何从模拟物理世界、重塑娱乐到最终解决能源危机、实现 AGI 并构建后稀缺时代的宏伟蓝图。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Demis Hassabis 在访谈中阐述了其“可学习宇宙”理论，并描绘了 AI 如何从模拟物理世界、重塑娱乐到最终解决能源危机、实现 AGI 并构建后稀缺时代的宏伟蓝图。",
  "summary": "文章深度剖析了 DeepMind 负责人德米斯·哈萨比斯对人工智能、宇宙本质及人类未来的前瞻性构想。哈萨比斯提出“可学习的宇宙”理论，认为自然界中的所有模式都可通过机器学习有效发现和建模，这为其 AlphaFold 等成就奠定哲学基础，并指引通向 AGI 的路径。他强调 AI 模拟物理世界的能力（如 VEO 对流体和光照的精准模拟），颠覆了传统具身智能理论。在交互娱乐领域，哈萨比斯设想 AI 将实现真正动态、个性化的开放世界游戏。对于 AGI 的实现，他预测五年内有 50%几率，并强调除规模外，“研究品味”和重大突破的关键性。最终，他将 AGI 视为解决能源危机、加速药物研发、开启“后稀缺时代”的终极工具。文章也警示了 AI 变革的巨大社会冲击，呼吁国际社会共同负责任地引入这项技术，并相信 AI 将帮助人类更好地理解自身意识。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "“可学习的宇宙”理论是 AI 能力和 AGI 的哲学基石",
      "explanation": "通过构建环境的精确模型，AI 能将指数级复杂问题转化为可解问题，暗示宇宙具备内在结构和可学习性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 通过被动观察可内化“直觉物理学”，挑战传统具身智能理论",
      "explanation": "视频生成模型 VEO 对物理现象的精准模拟，表明 AI 无需直接互动也能理解世界运作规律，令人惊讶。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 将彻底重塑交互娱乐，实现动态、个性化的无限世界",
      "explanation": "未来的游戏将打破“选择幻觉”，玩家与 AI 共同创造，极大降低创造门槛，颠覆娱乐产业。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AGI 的实现不仅依赖规模，更需要“研究品味”的突破性创新",
      "explanation": "识别并提出有价值的科学问题是更高层次的创造力，也是当前 AI 无法企及的关键，预示着 AGI 的挑战性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AGI 是解决人类文明根本挑战的“终极工具”，开启“后稀缺时代”",
      "explanation": "AI 有望加速药物研发、解决能源危机，使人类摆脱资源限制，但也将带来巨大的社会冲击，需提前应对。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "我的猜想是，自然界中可以生成或发现的任何模式，原则上都可以通过经典的机器学习算法有效地发现和建模。宇宙是一个信息系统，因此，P vs NP 本质上是一个物理学问题，我认为这是最根本的问题之一。",
    "选择正确的问题是科学中最难的部分。一个系统能否提出一个值得研究的猜想，比解决它要难得多。这是一种更高级的创造力，也是通往 AGI 路上的关键。今天的系统绝对无法做到这一点。",
    "在人类历史上，我们将第一次不受资源限制。如果我们能正确利用 AI 解决能源问题------无论是聚变还是太阳能------就能开启一个资源极大丰富的后稀缺时代，摆脱零和博弈。",
    "我不认为这是一场竞赛。重要的是，我们所有处于领先地位的人，都有责任为了人类的利益，安全地将这项令人难以置信的技术引入世界。我希望最终国际社群能够团结起来。",
    "AI 带来的变革，其影响可能相当于工业革命的 10 倍，但速度也快了 10 倍。这种影响与速度的乘积效应，将使社会更难应对。"
  ],
